85
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,700
They hadn't been hiding
in Jiangzhou all along.

86
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:17,780
The truth is, they had left Jiangzhou
for many years.

87
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,580
It must be some special event

88
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:21,460
that brings them back.

89
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:23,300
As for this special event,

90
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:25,140
