91
00:05:25,140 --> 00:05:26,300
rather than anything else.

92
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,300
Are you saying

93
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,060
that the reason why the three brothers

94
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:30,580
