95
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:32,620
is related to the death
of their relatives?

96
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:36,780
In other words, the three victimized families

97
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:37,640
are connected to the death

98
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,780
