99
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:40,820
Go on.

100
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,900
That's all I can think of for now.

101
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,540
Wait a minute.

102
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:46,540
Why do you tend to think

103
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:47,620
that their parents were both dead?

104
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:49,780
Because every time
when they committed a crime,

105
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:51,500
the victims' parents were present

106
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:52,540
without exception.

107
00:05:52,780 --> 00:05:54,420
This should be a form of pain substitution.

108
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:56,300
Subconsciously,

109
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,460
the three brothers

110
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:59,860
