201
00:09:55,780 --> 00:09:56,940
Then kill her.

202
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:00,140
- And me. I will be yours, too.
- You...

203
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,420
What are you hesitating for?

204
00:10:09,140 --> 00:10:11,180
This way, you give Mr. He hopes,

205
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:12,860
